body_html:
Could you please provide more detail - ideally all the details asked for in the new issue template. These include which version of TensorFlow you're using and instructions to reproduce the problem.

In general, the Java API is not tied to InceptionV3 and there have been uses of it with different models. Without the information asked for in the new issue template, it'll be hard for us to diagnose the problem.

Thanks!
